<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="incredible-adj">incredible <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'kredəbl/    美 /ɪn'kredəbl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>难以置信的；无法相信的；[口语] 极好的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Incredible! See how much he has changed now.
真令人难以置信！看看他现在变化多大啊！</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>incredibly /ɪn'kredəbli/ adv <br />
1. ★ <strong>[非正式用语] 极端地；非常地</strong>  </p>
<ol>
<li>★ <strong>[句子副词] 难以置信地</strong>  </li>
</ol></div>